$$
\begin{aligned}
\text{I:}\ (20\times 10) + (10\times 80) + 400 &= 1\,400\,\text{reais} \\
\text{II:}\ (20\times 30) + (10\times 50) + 200 &= 1\,300\,\text{reais} \\
\text{III:}\ (20\times 20) + (10\times 40) + 400 &= 1\,200\,\text{reais}
\end{aligned}
$$

O menor custo é o da autoescola III.
